            <li class="list-group-item">JWT Authentication – <a href="https://jwt.io/" target="_blank">jwt.io</a></li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Swagger / Swashbuckle – <a href="https://swagger.io/tools/swagger-ui/" target="_blank">swagger.io</a></li>
